OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirms must make            
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'adjustments' for          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmenopausal woman           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Employers could be sued if they do not 
OL,6, make "reasonable adjustments" for      
OL,7, menopausal women in the workplace,     
OL,8, according to the equalities watchdog.  
OL,10,FThe Equality and Human Rights          
OL,11,FCommission (EHRC) issued the guidance  
OL,12,Fto companies to clarify their legal    
OL,13,Fobligations to women.                  
OL,15,FAdjustments include letting women work 
OL,16,Ffrom home or wear cooler clothes.      
OL,18,FMenopause marks the end of a woman's   
OL,19,Fmenstrual cycles, and usually happens  
OL,20,Fin her 40s or 50s.                     
